# Comma-separated CORS origin patterns for the browser SPA (required for real deployments).
# Local default allows any localhost / 127.0.0.1 port (Vite, Docker mapped ports).
# Example production:
# CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGIN_PATTERNS=https://shop.example.com,https://www.shop.example.com
# CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGIN_PATTERNS=http://localhost:*,http://127.0.0.1:*
